nodes.text: Take Flight was a fathier female that mated with Doonium Strike, and gave birth to the fathier named Mynock Minute in 31 ABY as a result.

By around 34 ABY, Mynock Minute had become a racing fathier on the planet Cantonica. Take Flight was listed as the fathier's dam on race programs, including one collected by the Resistance mechanic Rose Tico and added to her diary.
Take Flight was first mentioned in the 2018 replica journal The Last Jedi: Rose Tico: Resistance Fighter, which was written by Jason Fry.
